## Usage

To use the hook in your project you must:

1. Import the component where you need it:

<Source
        language="javascript"
        code="import <%= name %> from '@byndyusoft-ui/<%= h.changeCase.paramCase(name) %>';"
/>

2. Call the hook and give it the desired args.

